Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:38.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91469,98684}{\i1}Nozomi ran away from DM Productions and\Nreturned back to Tōkyō to see her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:43.18,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:98684,103189}{\i1}She has to find job as soon\Nas possible to support her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:47.48,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:103189,107485}{\i1}Knowing that, despite\Nher strong passion for music
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.19,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:107485,110196}{\i1}she's made a decision\Nto become Miki's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:118120,120414}Today is your first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:120414,122041}I expect you do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:122041,123042}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:08.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:123042,128047}We're going to greet\Na few important people first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:17.72,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:129924,137723}{\t(6339,7799,2,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)}— Episode 14 —\NA Model Employee{NOTE:第14話\\N涙のワンピース}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.77,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:139683,142770}{\fad(2000,0)}Uchida Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:26.89,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:143229,146899}Yes, yes. Thank you as always.\NThe reason we're calling today…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:31.27,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:146899,151278}No, no. This absolutely has to go out\Nbefore the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:34.49,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:151278,154490}I can't find Kobashi Hikaru's\Ntapes anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.78,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:155324,156784}I'll go look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:156784,159078}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:159078,160287}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.12,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:160287,162123}Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.79,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:162123,163791}Ah, Miki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:47.04,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:163791,167044}About the photo shoot for the magazine\Nwe talked about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:47.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:167044,167670}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:50.29,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:167670,170297}It got delayed.\NWe'll do it on 10th in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:53.00,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:170297,173008}Sure thing.\NAnytime works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.17,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:173008,174176}Remember it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:174176,176011}Certainly. It's on 10th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.55,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:176011,178556}Is President in his office today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.05,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:178556,181058}President's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:08.56,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:181559,188566}Kōda Miki is a fantastic girl. She sings well,\Nmakes beautiful songs and has great looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.48,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:188566,190484}Kōda… Miki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.02,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:192236,194029}I'll keep her name in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.94,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:194029,195948}I'm so glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:20.70,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:195948,200703}You've always shown yourself\Nto be a man of your word, Kuga-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.03,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:200703,202037}Oh, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.29,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:203914,205291}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:205291,207585}Ha, speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.96,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:207585,210963}That's her, Kuga-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:42.14,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:217094,222141}This is Kuga Noboru, a famous TV critic.\NHere, say hello to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:222141,224476}My name is Kōda Miki.\NIt's a pleasure to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.02,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:225186,227021}Likewise. What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:229315,230774}She's my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.98,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:231400,232985}Assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:232985,235112}Let me introduce her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:58.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:235112,238407}She's Mine Nozomi-san, who's started\Nto work as my right arm from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:238407,241535}Please treat her\Nas you would treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:241535,243537}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:243537,246582}Wait a minute!\NWe've met before, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:246582,249418}Yes sir. I believe it was\Nin Mr. Egawa's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.79,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:249418,251795}Ah, that's right.\NNow I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:16.63,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:251795,256634}Correct me if I'm mistaken,\Nbut I heard that he's kicked you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:256634,257968}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.84,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:257968,259845}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.43,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:259845,262431}Is Mr. Egawa aware of this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.05,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:262431,264058}Ah, n-no, I haven't told him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:30.10,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:265643,270105}That's not good.\NHe's a rather eccentric person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.52,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:270105,273525}If he finds out,\Nit might strain our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:273525,275361}Miki-san, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:275361,278030}It's okay, Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:43.36,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:278030,283369}You have to take care of your\Nsick parents as well as your siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:283369,287081}I'll talk to Mr. Egawa.\NI'm sure he'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.41,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:287081,290417}I see. I just hope\Neverything works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.29,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:290417,293295}I'll ask my mother\Nto speak with him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.29,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:293295,295297}Please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.54,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:295297,297549}I'm ready to get scolded\Nif it's for my friend's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.30,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:298968,302304}You don't have to worry\Nabout anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.30,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:302304,306308}All you have to do is to think\Nabout doing your job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:306308,307476}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:13.31,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:309770,313315}Your story is very touching.\NIt'd sell great in magazines for young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:20.65,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:315401,320656}See? I didn't lie to you, Kuga-chan.\NI told you she was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.07,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:320656,322074}Alright, Miki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.24,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:322074,323242}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.37,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:323242,326370}Take this girl and show her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:30.24,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:326370,330249}Tell your story to everyone.\NYou'll earn a lot of sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:36.08,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:330249,336088}It'll show that the debuting singer Kōda Miki\Nis a gentle person. It'll help build your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.42,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:336088,338424}It's going to be a wild success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:43.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:338424,343512}Oh, I'm embarrassed now… I didn't want\Nto sound like I'm trying to impress you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:47.89,Default,Kuga Noboru,0,0,0,,{TIME:343512,347891}You're right, it's better if the girl told her story\Nherself. It'd be more believable that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.81,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:347891,350811}You have a point, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.14,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:350811,353147}Mine-kun, this is\Nyour new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:353147,355065}Huh? My new assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:06:01.57,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:355065,361572}An assistant must do everything she can\Nto help the star she's working for build her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:08.20,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:363240,368203}{\fad(1000,0)}"Weekly Young" Editorial Department{NOTE:週刊ヤング編集部}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.20,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:364408,368203}As Uchida Productions, we're very thankful\Nfor your patronage to our fresh singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:369538,373834}I will never forget the sincere kindness\Nthat Miki-san has shown me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:373834,375836}Please, don't be\Nso formal, Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.75,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:375836,379757}What do you think, boss?\NCould we use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.13,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:379757,381133}It's a moving story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.76,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:381133,382760}Hmm. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:26.76,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:381508,386764}{\fad(1000,0)}"Entertainment Times"\NEditing Department{NOTE:芸能タイムス編集部}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:26.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:382760,386764}If it wasn't for Miki-san,\NI don't know what'd happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:387473,389725}How could I leave you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:389725,393771}The only hope you had left\Nwas to become a waitress in a local bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:394772,396774}What? A waitress?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.65,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:396774,398650}You're able to do\Nmuch better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.98,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:398650,400986}Look this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.19,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:400986,402196}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:47.03,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:401695,407034}{\fad(700,0)}Orion Records Studio{NOTE:オリオンレコードスタジオ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:47.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:403072,407034}Miki-san took the risk of upsetting Mr. Egawa\Njust to keep me in her service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:51.74,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:407493,411747}Don't worry. I'll put in a good word\Nfor you with Mr. Egawa myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:57.54,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:411747,417544}{\fad(700,0)}Sun TV Talent Clock{NOTE:太陽テレビ タレントクロック}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:413540,417544}I left Mr. Egawa's house without\Nasking for his permission, and Miki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:02.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:418462,422091}I couldn't just stand by and\Nhad to step in and try to fix things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:424051,427388}{\i1}The more I talk to all those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:427388,429681}{\i1}the more painful it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:13.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:429681,433560}{\i1}I didn't want to tell anyone that\NI was driven out of Mr. Egawa's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:435020,438899}{\i1}But it's my job\Nas Miki-san's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:438899,440442}{\i1}I have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:440442,442694}{\i1}I have to stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.36,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:444738,448367}Poor Nozomi-san. Her tour\Nin the countryside was a total fiasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:32.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:448367,452079}But she had enough common sense\Nto admit her mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:36.70,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:452079,456708}I will try to do everything I can\Nto get Mr. Egawa to accept her new role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.58,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:456708,457584}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.21,Default,Newspaper,0,0,0,,{TIME:458669,460212}Nohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:462172,464591}I still have to thank you\Nfor everything you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.84,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:464591,466844}Oh, d-don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.97,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:466844,469972}The things that this young lady says\Nare nothing but tall tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.43,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:469972,471432}Tall tales?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.05,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:471432,474059}What do you mean, Nohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.68,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:474059,477688}Mine-kun's tour in the countryside,\Nrather than a total fiasco,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.98,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:477688,479982}was much more of a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.11,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:479982,483110}At least that's what I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:11.32,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:486530,491326}There was no end to DM Pro's bastards' greed.\NThey exploited her all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:15.28,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:491326,495289}But wherever she went,\NMine-kun has enchanted the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.54,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:495289,499543}Her managers got the money,\Nand she had the audience's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:499543,503088}But Nozomi-san herself\Nadmits that—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.21,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:503088,506216}…she's got kicked out of Mr. Egawa's house?\NIs this what you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.88,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:506216,508886}– But it's the truth.\N– Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:32.38,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:508886,512389}Yes, it's a fact that Egawa-san's\Ndriven Mine-kun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.43,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:512389,515434}But he's regretting\Nthat decision lately a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.35,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:515434,516351}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:516351,518270}You're not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:518270,521106}Nohara-san!\NYou don't have to defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:521106,523692}I really was wrong, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.27,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:523692,525277}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:49.78,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:525277,529781}You're wasting your potential being\Nher secretary. Better quit this job soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.32,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:529781,532326}This kid possesses\Nsome amazing qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.74,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:532326,533744}I can vouch for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.07,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:533744,535078}Mine Nozomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:535078,536371}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.70,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:536371,538707}If Jun-chan says so,\Nit must be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.92,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:541877,545923}What do you think of starting over\Nunder another teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:545923,549009}It sounds good, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:16.14,Default,Important other guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:552387,556141}If you wish, I can introduce you\Nto another teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:556141,557518}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:567236,569404}Remember what they told you\Nat the record company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:569404,572824}You're my assistant.\NYou're supposed to stay behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:572824,574243}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:38.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:574243,578163}In the end you always take all the praise,\Nwhile I have to stay on the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:578163,581208}How about you say\Nsomething to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.79,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:581208,583794}After everything I did for you!\NYou ingrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:584711,585963}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:585963,587798}I'll be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:52.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:587798,592219}Anyway, you're supposed to be my assistant.\NWhat's with these flashy clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:592219,594096}You mean, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:594096,595389}Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.93,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:595389,596932}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:596932,598100}Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:598100,599893}Here? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:07.94,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:603438,607943}Buy the most plain-looking dress\Nin that store over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:607943,609069}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:609069,611738}It will be your uniform\Nfrom tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:611738,614825}But what about the money?\NI can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:614825,616827}Just get it on credit for the Kōdas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:22.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:616827,622499}My dad has unlimited credit\Nin every department store in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:622499,624918}Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:631174,633385}– How about this?\N– It suits you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:633385,634636}And this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.59,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{TIME:634636,636597}It looks a little plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:636597,638015}All right, I'll get this one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.26,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{TIME:638432,639266}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.43,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:639933,642436}– Err, ma'am?\N– What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.39,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:642436,644396}Perhaps I'm mistaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:48.85,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:644396,648859}but I don't think you have a deal\Nwith that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:648859,651778}Oh? I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:56.36,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,{TIME:652321,656366}Then we'll forward the payment\Nto Kōda Daijirō-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:59.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:656366,659536}Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:670589,671965}Can I help you, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:15.26,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:671965,675260}Are you the customer who has shopped\Nin the name of Kōda-san on the sixth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:675260,677137}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:20.68,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:677137,680682}We don't have a credit account\Nfor anyone named Kōda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:681266,682601}That can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:682601,684936}Sir, this must be\Na misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.10,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:684936,686104}You're coming with me.
Comment: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:32.27,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:692277,692277}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.61,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:695030,697616}There's no one named\NKōda Daijirō on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:697616,699284}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:43.16,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:699284,703163}This list contains information on every\Nregistered client that ever shopped at Edo-Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.45,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:703163,705457}There is no error.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:51.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:707793,711213}Please call this number\Nand explain the situation to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.25,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:711213,714257}Whose number is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:714257,716593}The third number from the top,\NKōda Daijirō.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.47,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:718929,720472}"Edo-Ya"? A department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.30,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:720472,723308}We have no contract with them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.64,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:724893,727646}What?! Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.56,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:727646,730565}She bought in our name\Nwithout so much as asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:14.11,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:730565,734111}No, we don't want to have\Nanything to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.65,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:736071,737656}They said they don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:737656,740325}I can't believe it.\NIt's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.03,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:740325,742035}What misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.95,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:742035,744955}– Why don't you just apologize?\N– I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:744955,746540}But please, let me\Nmake one more call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:29.00,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:746540,749000}I can't believe how stubborn you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:749000,751211}I'm sorry, I'm borrowing\Nthis for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.67,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:751211,753672}It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:760804,761722}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.93,Default,Kōda's receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:761722,763932}{\i1}Sorry for making you wait.\NThis is the president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:47.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:763932,767352}My name is Mine Nozomi.\NI'd like to speak with Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.73,Default,Kōda's receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:767352,769730}{\i1}May I ask what this is regarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:52.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:769730,772107}If you tell him that Mine Nozomi\Nhas called, he'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.44,Default,Kōda's receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:772107,774443}{\i1}I'm sorry, but the president\Nis in a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.32,Default,Kōda's receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:774443,778321}{\i1}Do you want me to\Npass a message to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:01.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:778321,781074}No. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:03.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:781074,783535}I'm so sorry, Nozomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:784578,785871}Kōda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.54,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:787497,789541}"Kōda-san"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.87,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:791376,793879}I'm sorry, Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:17.17,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:793879,797174}I was mistaken\Nand I put you in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:797174,798759}I only realized this\Nalong my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:22.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:798759,802012}It's no problem.\NThank you, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:802012,804514}Relax. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:804514,806808}I apologize. I'm Kōda Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.47,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:806808,809478}D-Don't tell me…\NFrom that Kōda family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:809478,812272}Yes. My father's name is Daijirō.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:812272,816401}I apologize for letting a simple mistake\Ncause you all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:40.61,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:816401,820614}No, no. Everything's fine as long\Nas you're happy with it, Kōda-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:43.57,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:820614,823575}I'll pay for it right away.\NHow much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.45,Default,Interrogator,0,0,0,,{TIME:823575,826453}It'll be an honor, ma'am.\NIt's 1,100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:826453,828163}I see. It's very cheap.
