Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.56,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035687,1037564}Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039816,1040859}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.02,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040859,1043028}Ah, your next lesson? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.32,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043028,1046322}I've brought someone with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.74,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048033,1050744}No… Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050744,1053371}Good morning, Sune-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:36.58,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053371,1056583}Y-You're Kōda-san's assistant now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.33,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056583,1058334}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060545,1062338}Do you even need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062338,1065091}I just hired Nozomi-san\Nbecause she asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.21,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065675,1068219}I didn't ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.93,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068219,1070930}Come on in.\NYou can't stay in the door.
