Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:55.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072390,1075602}You can't blame her. She was\Nkicked out of this place before, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075602,1078980}Give me the bag\Nand wait for me in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.56,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1078980,1080565}– Here.\N– Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:05.36,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080565,1085361}Nozomi-chan is your assistant now,\Nso she can meet Master normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085361,1086863}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.44,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086863,1089449}As Kōda Miki's assistant,\Nyou need to stay close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.66,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089449,1092660}Once Master sees you,\Nmaybe he'll even change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.87,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092660,1093870}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093870,1094579}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095330,1098958}Hmph. Okay, but remember that\Nyou're my assistant, no more and no less.
