Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.83,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100376,1101836}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101836,1102545}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:31.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106091,1111679}{\i1}I thought I'd never come back,\Nbut I can be here again as Miki-san's assistant.
