Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.69,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122899,1124692}You're not alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124692,1127403}I brought my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137872,1140083}Hurry up and give me the score.
