Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.12,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260662,1263122}Listen to Mr. Egawa's piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.25,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263122,1265250}He's happy that you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265250,1266918}What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.58,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266918,1269587}Call me when you need something.
