Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314841,1317719}You were amazing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.92,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317719,1319929}Really, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:03.85,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319929,1323850}Yes. The way you were today,\Nyou're ready to make your debut.
