Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:34.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351794,1354422}{\i1}I hate Kōda Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:38.63,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354422,1358635}{\i1}But the way she is now,\NI hate Mine Nozomi even more.
