Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363306,1366100}{\i1}She's sunk so low\Nover a few pennies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:53.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370271,1373650}{\i1}I said it to her before. If she does this,\Nit'll be the end of the both of them.
